<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>zhàn qǐ lái dōng fāng de rén 迦南96</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 zhàn qǐ lái zhàn qǐ lái dōng fāng de rén, zhàn qǐ lái zhàn qǐ lái wǒ men zhè qún rén,
 hēi yǎn jīng hēi tóu fā huáng pí fū, wǒ men yǒng yuǎn shì shén ài de rén.
 dài zhe shǐ mìng xiàng sì fāng zǒu qù, nà lǐ xū yào jiù zài nà lǐ zhā gēn,
 bù qiú nà shū shì de shēng huó ān yì de jiā yī gè xīn yuàn qiǎng jiù líng hún.</lyrics>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<hymn_number>96</hymn_number>
</song>